node.text: Faye’s room is finished, and we’re loving it! #ad We put together this little video showing how the room came together over time and also how I used @Honey to shop a mix of save-splurge, high-low pieces. Manually searching for promo codes is a thing of the past—Honey is free to install and just takes two clicks. Go to joinhoney.com/clj before doing any more online shopping. 🖤 #honeyapp #honey #fayesroom

node.text: Salad doesn’t always feel “wintery” to me, but once the holidays pass and my body can’t take anymore sugar, I just need something fresh. But I also like to eat seasonally, when I can. This Winter Salad features a lot of vegetables (root and otherwise), shaved super thin, and dressed in a sweet potato dressing with mild hint of curry. Full recipe at chrislovesjulia.com. #chriscooks #salad #dairyfree #grainfree #glutenfree #healthyeating

node.text:
HOSTING DOESN’T HAVE TO LOOK LIKE THIS.

You don’t need a table for 20, fine china, a chef husband, a photogenic house or even a core group of friends to entertain. 

Opening your door to have people over can be simple, impactful, and rewarding because you’re creating memories and attachments to your home—and falling in love with it in the process. 

Maybe it’s a backyard hang, or game night or watch party or, sure, a dinner party! Whatever you do, it should make you happy. That’s the entire goal. We’re sharing a bunch of low-stress tips for entertaining today on chrislovesjulia.com!! Link in profile. #cljsummerschool #cljdiningroom #lovewhereyoulive #entertaining
